Requirements
------------

On Ubuntu 12.04 we need git and boto:
$ apt-get install git
$ apt-get install python-pip python-dev
$ pip install --upgrade pip

If doesn't work logout and sudo again:
$ pip install --upgrade virtualenv
$ pip install --upgrade boto

This is all it takes to backup all non-root volumes:
$ mkdir -p 9apps/tools && cd 9apps/tools
$ git clone git@github.com:9apps/backups.git
$ cd backups
$ python backup/backup.py setup